                John Neihardt<lb/>
                Rte 7<lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">Columbia, Mo.</hi>
                </ab>
                
                <ab type="postmark">COLUMBIA, MO. OCT 20 330 PM 1959</ab>
                <figure>
